Color.description:
Average similarity of the maximum similarity between pairs of colors. Pairs are created using the shortest color list and the colors in the other list.
Similarity between every pair of colors is computed using [Delta E 2000 color difference function](http://www.colorwiki.com/wiki/Delta_E:_The_Color_Difference#dE2000), which is a standard measurement that quantifies the difference between two colors that appear on a screen
